socialpoints

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
social points - how much communication you can perform
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The amount of (particularly) loud communication you can do in a given time
frame is governed by your social points.

Shout a lot and your social points go down, don't shout and they recover.

Your maximum number social points will increase with age.

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
hitpoints, guildpoints
.EP
